{
  "texts": [
    "Correspondingly, we distinguished between incorrectness and harmfulness in responses.",
    "Incorrect responses may include suggestions for superfluous diagnostic procedures or contain requests for irrelevant patient information.",
    "Conversely, harmful responses, while also incorrect, were determined by clinical judgment as potentially deleterious, such as advising suboptimal or contraindicated treatments.",
    "Furthermore, we assessed the completeness of the responses.",
    "For this purpose, we identified multiple specific keywords and terms for each unique medical scenario."
  ]
}